snippet.title: Amber Heard Interview: Aquaman Star Talks Spanglish and Big Kid Jason Momoa
snippet.description:
Amber Heard stars alongside Jason Momoa in James Wan's AQUAMAN. The native Texan is fluent in Spanish and she's using her bilingual skills to talk about being super soaked in her costume, Jason Momoa's big personality and why she's not diving into an ocean anytime soon.
